{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_01","textHome":"那么，请让我再次自我介绍……我的名字是日@向茉莉！我住在一个叫鬼灯市的地方。在那@里，我一直和遥香、千里和亚里纱她们一起@作为魔法少女活动。我不是很了解神滨，所@以如果你愿意告诉我各种事情就好了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.7,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_17","textHome":"……小兔子挂件的挂绳……断掉了……但是，@一直把它放在房间里也太可怜了……我还是@去找找新的挂绳吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_18","textHome":"快看快看！我试着换了一下小兔子的挂绳。为@了让这次的挂绳不会断掉，我特意选了根很@结实的。……但是，颜色是不是有点太朴素@了？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_19","textHome":"感觉，气息比之前要更容易探查到了。尽管依@靠我吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_20","textHome":"虽然这份力量是为了战斗而存在的，但真不想@用它来伤害他人啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_21","textHome":"我并不喜欢争斗。但是，我也知道，有的时候@不战斗就不行。所以，能变强我也很高兴哦@。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_22","textHome":"“如果有感到困扰的人……请一定要去帮助他@哦。”虽然不记得这是谁对我说的了……但@是在我脑中，它作为非常重要的话语而残留@下来了。我觉得，现在的自己应该离那个无@法想起的人稍微接近一些了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_23","textHome":"我觉得，自己作为魔法少女已经变得十分强大@了。之后该思考的，就是该如何使用这份力@量了吧。我……想要成为困扰的人可以依赖@的存在。为了让我能成为那样的人，请你一@定要见证下去哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_24","textHome":"你是来见我的吗？诶嘿嘿，如果是这样，那真@是让人高兴啊。今天要做什么呢？如果能和@你一起玩，不管玩什么都肯定很开心吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_25","textHome":"早上好！我接下来要和千里一起去叫亚里纱起@床。这已经成为我每天必做的事情了呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_26","textHome":"快看快看！我今天的便当是卡通便当哦！看起@来就像蔬菜的森林包围着小兔子形状的饭团@，怎么样？可爱吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_02","textHome":"初次见面！我是日向茉莉！要是能友好相处就@好了啊——！毕竟，朋友还是越多越让人开@心嘛！我们先试着聊聊各种事情如何？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_27","textHome":"我非常喜欢晚霞。逐渐西沉的太阳，受到那份@光辉照射而发光的云。还有，仍然蔚蓝的东@方的天空……许多颜色混杂在一起，非常漂@亮。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_28","textHome":"呼哇～已经这么晚了啊……虽然我明白要早点@睡才行……但是，星星很漂亮，所以真想再@稍微看一会儿啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_29","textHome":"我很喜欢上学哦。毕竟，这样就能见到大家，@也能通过学习学到很多不知道的东西嘛！今@天会有什么样的事情等着我呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_30","textHome":"莫非，你接下来要去讨伐魔女吗？那样的话，@我也能一起去吗？我很擅长支援，所以肯定@能派上用场的哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_31","textHome":"是叫无尽镜界吗？那个有长得和魔法少女们一@模一样的人出没的地方。难得来了一趟神滨@市……去那里看看吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_32","textHome":"哇——！有好多魔法少女耶！我比起战斗，还@是更想和大家好好相处、交上朋友啊……毕@竟，那样会更加开心嘛。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_33","textHome":"听说改天千里要参加比赛哦！我们也去给她加@油吧！……嗯？你问是什么的比赛？……啊@！千里是游泳社的成员。我好像没说过呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_34","textHome":"在考试之前，我也会和大家一起学习哦。遥香@虽然就算不进行考前学习也很有余裕，但她@总是会陪我们一起呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403200,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_35","textHome":"有顶帐的床很稀奇吗？之前亚里纱是这么对我@说的……但是，遥香的床上好像也有哦。你@觉得是什么样的呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_36","textHome":"娃娃机的奖品里面有个特别可爱的玩偶。虽然@我没抓到，但是亚里纱帮我抓到了哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_03","textHome":"不了解的城市真是让人激动不已！真想看见更@多不同的东西啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_37","textHome":"我收到了一些茉莉花茶。对方说是因为茉莉花@和我的名字特别配哦！味道真的好好闻啊…@…赶紧泡一点看看吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_38","textHome":"我们班里来了一位转学生。听说，她叫作天乃@铃音。我们还没有好好说过话，所以，下次@要不要试着向她搭一下话呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_39","textHome":"我的家人？现在，我只和爸爸在一起生活哦。@因为妈妈已经去世了，我也没有兄弟姐妹。@如果有兄弟姐妹的话，该是什么样的感觉呢@？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_40","textHome":"在过去……我的眼睛是看不见东西的。拜次所@赐，我也没有什么出门的聚会。所以，现在@能遇见各种各样的东西，我真的很高兴。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_41","textHome":"……诶？这本绘本……总感觉我有见过……嗯@——……是不是在过去有人为我读过呢……@虽然很怀念，但也有一种奇怪的感觉……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403200}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_42","textHome":"虽然不喜欢战斗，但是……嗯，我会加油的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_43","textHome":"明明要是能和大家友好相处就好了啊……"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_44","textHome":"呼……如果有帮上大家的忙就好了啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_45","textHome":"……嗯，已经没有敌人的气息了呢。辛苦了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_46","textHome":"结束了——！来，一起回去吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_04","textHome":"神滨真是个不可思议的地方啊。感觉还有很多@这样的地方在等着我！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_05","textHome":"我绝对不会忘记今天的事情的哦。毕竟，这是@重要的回忆嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_13","textHome":"哎？我感觉，自己稍微变强了一点！你不这么@觉得吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_14","textHome":"好厉害！我变得前所未有地强大了！谢谢你。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_15","textHome":"再跟我说说更多各种各样的事情吧！真想通过@这样变得更加要好啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4032_00_16","textHome":"这个小兔子的挂件很可爱吧？这是我很中意的@东西！我把它挂在包上，所以它一直都和我@在一起！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403200,"motion":300}]}]},"version":3}